---
title: Vegan Sweet Potato & Onion Sandos with Guacamole plus a Cucumber & Spinach Salad
description: Are you on board for another brilliant vegan dinner idea from our gifted chefs? Savory and tender spice-roasted sweet potatoes are layered with caramelized onion and baby spinach on pan-fried sourdough slathered in guacamole and vegan chipotle mayo. Add a bright spinach side salad with crispy cukes and crunchy almonds and you’ve got a wholesome ticket to flavorville on the brunch, lunch, or dinner express.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/vegan-sweet-potato-onion-sandos-aafee7b2.jpg
pdf: https://www.hellofresh.com/recipecards/card/vegan-sweet-potato-onion-sandos-63aa8d233fcd7531810f3f25-7845cb6c.pdf
cuisine: North America
