  calories: 810 kcal
  fat: 50 g
  saturated fat: 7 g
  carbohydrates: 88 g
  sugar: 14 g
  protein: 13 g
  fiber: 10 g
  sodium: 880 mg
course: main course
author: HelloFresh
servings: 2
source: https://www.hellofresh.com/recipes/vegan-sweet-potato-onion-sandos-63aa8d233fcd7531810f3f25
time required: 30 minutes
---

Adjust rack to top position and preheat oven to 425 degrees. Wash and dry produce.

Peel and slice @sweet potato{1} into ¼-inch-thick rounds. Toss on a #baking sheet{} with a drizzle of oil, half the @Fry Seasoning{1%tablespoon}, @salt{}, and @pepper{}. Roast on top rack until browned and tender, ~{18-20%minutes}.

Meanwhile, halve, peel, and thinly slice @red onion{1}. Roughly chop @cilantro{¼%ounce}. Halve @mini cucumber{1} lengthwise; slice into ¼-inch-thick half-moons.

Heat a large drizzle of @cooking oil{1%tablespoon} in a medium, preferably nonstick, pan over medium-high heat. Add onion; cook, stirring occasionally, until browned and softened, ~{8-10%minutes}. Add @sugar{1%teaspoon} and a splash of water; cook until caramelized, ~{2-3%minutes} more. Season with salt and pepper.

Meanwhile, in a large #bowl{}, combine @white wine vinegar{5%teaspoon}, cilantro, cucumber, @sugar{½%teaspoon}, @olive oil{2%tablespoon}, salt, and pepper. Set aside.

Heat @olive oil{1%tablespoon} in a large pan over medium heat. Add @sourdough bread{4%slices}; toast until golden brown, ~{2-3%minutes} per side. Transfer to a #cutting board{}.

Add ¾ of the @baby spinach{5%ounce} and @sliced almonds{½%ounce} to bowl with cucumber mixture; toss to combine. Season with salt and pepper to taste.

Spread half the sourdough slices with @vegan chipotle mayonnaise{2%tablespoon}. Spread remaining sourdough slices with @guacamole{4%tablespoon}. Fill with even layers of sweet potato, onion, and as much remaining spinach as you like. Close sandwiches and cut in half crosswise.

Divide sandwiches and salad between plates and serve.

> Add a bright spinach side salad with crispy cukes and crunchy almonds and you've got a wholesome ticket to flavorville on the brunch, lunch, or dinner express.